description:
Added Vocals with lyrics and Note names, added Bass track to mimic effects, small BPM changes, added Sections, fixed number of bars, combined Guitar tracks
Guitar: Edited Intro, fixed Riffs, improved fingering, edited Chords before Chorus, added Chords in the Chorus, improved Solo, added a Chord before the Bridge, fixed fingering in Bridge and last Chord, added Riff in Interlude, edited the last Chord and added the Slide
Actually the Hammer-Ons in this song are done only by Tim and not Tom
Bass: Added Chords to Intro, fixed fingerings, added Hammer-Ons, added Chords before the Chorus, added a detail before the Bridge, fixed fingering in Bridge and added Hammer-Ons and Slides, fixed last Notes and added the Slide
Drums: Improved Toms and Snares in Intro and Interlude, added Kicks to Pre-Verse and Solo, edited cymbals in Verse 1, removed some cymbals from Chorus (he plays 1 crash, at least live), fixed transition before Chorus 2, added ghost Snares to Bridge and changed some cymbals
title: Cochise
